#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn55.74"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.74:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.74:0.2"
msgid "7. Mahāpaññavagga "
msgstr "7. Great Wisdom "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.74:0.3"
msgid "74. Nibbedhikapaññāsutta "
msgstr "74. Penetrating Wisdom "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn55.74:1.1"
msgid "“… Nibbedhikapaññatāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when four things are developed and cultivated they lead to penetrating wisdom. "

msgctxt "sn55.74:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn55.74:1.3"
msgid "Sappurisasaṃsevo, saddhammassavanaṃ, yonisomanasikāro, dhammānudhammappaṭipatti—"
msgstr "Associating with good people, listening to the true teaching, proper attention, and practicing in line with the teaching. "

msgctxt "sn55.74:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā nibbedhikapaññatāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "When these four things are developed and cultivated they lead to penetrating wisdom.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.74:1.5"
msgid "Terasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.74:1.6"
msgid "Mahāpaññavaggo sattamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn55.74:2.1"
msgid "Mahā puthu vipula gambhīraṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.74:2.2"
msgid "Appamatta bhūri bāhullaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.74:2.3"
msgid "Sīgha lahu hāsa javana, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.74:2.4"
msgid "Tikkha nibbedhikāya cāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn55.74:2.5"
msgid "Sotāpattisaṃyuttaṃ ekādasamaṃ. "
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on Stream-Entry, the eleventh section."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
